title: 10/13 BONUS! Mailbag and DFS Advice (Recorded Fri.)
description:
Need some help with your Week 6 lineup? Adam and Jamey will answer your start or sit questions and grade your trades after updating you on the latest injury news. We'll also tell you what our FanDuel lineups are looking like (32:30).
